  "keyFeatures": [
    "RAG-based solution retrieval with 1800+ pre-generated coding solutions",
    "HNSW indexing for fast similarity search (15s query time)",
    "Dual-mode inference: general and reasoning modes using Ollama",
    "Conversation history with configurable memory buffer",
    "Metadata filtering by difficulty, topics, and companies",
    "Flask web interface with real-time streaming responses",
